node.text:
Lighting is key 🔑 This is the all-new @LumeCube Edge Light - the first desk light designed to double as a Video Call light for Zoom Calls (it flips up and acts as a Broadcast Light to illuminate you when on a Zoom Call, then flips down to illuminate your workspace). 

Edge Light features 5 rotating pivot points which allow the light to rotate anywhere on your desk. No more traditional stationary desk lamps, just pure frictionless maneuverability around your desk!

Plus - it’s designed with Premium Edge-Lit technology, a new LED technology which makes it easy on the eyes, allows the light to be sleek in design (thinner than an iPhone), and creates a soft glow that flatters everyone on camera!

Check out @LumeCube for more details on the new Edge light and how you can get your hands on it!

#LumeCube #LumeCubePartner
